hackathon-description-text: The SCHS Hackathon will be full of coding, learning, food, prizes, and even a little competition! It is open to high school students around the district that want to learn and have fun with their passions in technology.

hackathon-prizes.prize-content: $25 Best Buy gift cards for each person on team.

hackathon-judging-criteria.judging-criterion: Hacks will be judged based on innovation, creativity, and programming goodness.
